Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:10.58,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}We erase it from our memories
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:17.27,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}You can't escape I only know this secret with you
