Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.52,0:21:32.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}Close your eyes I'll be anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:40.60,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}I can't live this life without you by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.69,0:21:46.73,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\an9\fs16}「I'll believe..」
