Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:35.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}時の流れ見送る度に薄れる感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.69,0:22:40.98,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}たけどこれ以上見過ごしたくなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:41.55,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Back and forth　心中叫んでやまない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:45.38,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}time over　消えていく残像それは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:50.40,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あなたそのものだから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.99,0:22:50.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}So now that you & I
